'''''The Life Monitor''''' was a newsgrid service that was run and managed by [[Cindel Towani]] during the early years of the [[New Republic/Legends|New Republic]]. [[Hiram Drayson/Legends|Hiram Drayson]] called in a favor from Cindel, hoping to run a story that would bolster [[Leia Organa Solo/Legends|Leia Organa Solo's]] appearance during the [[Black Fleet Crisis]].

